  "title": "chore(ts-migration): adds api extrator for public definitions files and strip Internals",
  "body": "This pull request **now** uses api extractor for validating the public files we are exporting instead of a single file.\r\n\r\nHere is an example:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1029\" alt=\"Screenshot 2020-04-08 at 14 47 41\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5457236/78785733-f2e7d380-79a7-11ea-83c1-bee05724a916.png\">\r\n\r\nIn addition, it adds **stripInternals** option the tsconfig file, so we can hide some internals from the public API.\r\n",
